dispensary.name: Honeycomb Cannabis - St. Paul
dispensary.description:
To produce the sweetest honey, bees look to the best flowers...

We take our flower seriously at Honeycomb and pride ourselves on stocking a wide selection of cannabis products, whether you’re after bud, pre-rolls, edibles, beverages, capsules, vapes, accessories, tinctures, oils or any/all of the above.

Daily CBD user? We’ve got you covered? Special-occasions THC consumer? You bet! After all, your satisfaction is our “bee’s knees.” (Groan all you want…)

If you’re looking to #findyourbestbuzz, honeycomb is here to help.

products.name: CYPRESS CRAFT : MIMOSA PRE ROLLS (SATIVA) - 2 X 0.5g
products.description: Fragrant, flavorful notes of orange and skunk permeate this powerhouse of a strain from Cypress Craft in Manitoba. Equal parts uplifting and euphoric, the effects are as complex and varied as the delightful citrus aroma you'll be greeted with when you open the tube.
products.strainDescription: Mimosa, also known as "Purple Mimosa," is a hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing Clementine with Purple Punch. In small doses, this strain produces happy, level-headed effects that will leave you feeling uplifted and motivated enough to take on any mundane task. In large doses, Mimosa may make you feel sleepy and relaxed. This strain has a strong aroma and flavor that reminds you of its namesake, with notes of fruit and citrus flavors bursting through. Medical marijuana patients choose this strain to help relieve symptoms associated with depression and stress. Mimosa is a staple from the Tangie family. Breeder Symbiotic Genetics has released a refined Mimosa dubbed Mimosa v6.

products.name: RAW WOOD POKERS 113MM
products.description: RAW Wood Pokers help you fill and pack RAW cones with super ease move. RAW Wood Poker is all-natural wooden device.

products.name: KING PALM CORN HUSK FILTER - BERRY TERP
products.description: Berry Terps Filter Tips from King Palm are a safe and easy way to add some refreshing mint flavor to your favorite rolling papers, blunt wraps, and cigarillos. Made from natural corn husk, each filter tip has a built-in flavor pearl made with terpene-infused food grade essential oils that provide a subtle flavor that complements your dry herb. Squeeze and pop the filter to activate the flavor; tips will taste unflavored until the pearl bursts. Each pack of tips includes two individual 7mm filters that can be used to roll up a joint or blunt.

products.name: RANDY'S SCREENS - METAL - STAINLESS STEEL 0.625
products.description: Randy's Mesh Screens are a simple and effective filtration system created with the highest grade of materials available to ensure an elevated smoking experience for any user. The Mesh Screens keeps uninterrupted air flow while keeping your precious herb exactly where it belongs. Stainless steel is an unmatched material that is known for its high melting point.  This is what makes it so durable when undergoing constant temperature changes.

products.name: RAW CLASSIC HEMP SINGLE WIDE SINGLE WINDOW ROLLING PAPERS
products.description: RAW Classic is where it all began. The launch of RAW Classic transformed the smoking culture to a focus on quality and true naturalness. RAW is crafted from vegan, unbleached plant fibers and finished with the purest natural tree sap gumline.  Each leaf is watermarked with our proprietary criss-cross steam imprint that helps prevent runs and maintain a smooth, even burn.

products.name: RAW WIDE PRE-ROLLED UNBLEACHED TIPS
products.description: RAW Wide pre-rolled tips are designed to allow for a bigger roll and a bigger smoke. We carefully cut and pre-roll each tip to ensure a perfectly round smooth tip.

products.name: CLIPPER ROUND PLASTIC JET FLAME SOFT BLACK LIGHTER
products.description: Clipper windproof jet flame lighters, use the removable flint housing as a poker tool to tightly pack the material inside so your flame will stay ablaze!

products.name: BLUE ZIG ZAG ROLLING PAPERS
products.description:
A free-burning take on the original iconic Zig-Zag White Kutcorners. Easy to roll, with a faster burn.

Features:

70mm x 38mm
Made using Natural Flax Plant Fibers
100% Natural Gum Arabic

products.name: ULTRA THIN ZIG ZAG ROLLING PAPERS
products.description: Ultra-thin weight means less paper for minimal ash and no paper taste. Slow-burning and easy to roll.

products.name: BIC MAXI FLICK YOUR BIC LIGHTER
products.description:
Bic Maxi Flick Your Bic Lighters come in a wide selection of vibrant colors and eye-catching designs, making it easy to express your mood and personal style! Quality and safety are built into every step of the BIC Lighter production process.
Features: Child-resistant, safe and reliable lighters, 100% quality inspected up to 2 times the lights, Every BIC quality lighter undergoes more than 50 separate, automatic quality checks during the manufacturing process. The Mesh Screens keeps uninterrupted air flow while keeping your precious herb exactly where it belongs. Stainless steel is an unmatched material that is known for its high melting point.  This is what makes it so durable when undergoing constant temperature changes.

products.name: RAW CLASSIC HEMP SINGLE WIDE SINGLE WINDOW ROLLING PAPERS
products.description: RAW Classic is where it all began. The launch of RAW Classic transformed the smoking culture to a focus on quality and true naturalness. RAW is crafted from vegan, unbleached plant fibers and finished with the purest natural tree sap gumline.  Each leaf is watermarked with our proprietary criss-cross steam imprint that helps prevent runs and maintain a smooth, even burn.

products.name: RAW WIDE PRE-ROLLED UNBLEACHED TIPS

Bic Maxi Flick Your Bic Lighters come in a wide selection of vibrant colors and eye-catching designs, making it easy to express your mood and personal style! Quality and safety are built into every step of the BIC Lighter production process.

Unique lighters that come in a variety of different colors, prints and designs.

products.name: CYPRESS CRAFT : MIMOSA PRE ROLLS (SATIVA) - 2 X 0.5g
products.description: Fragrant, flavorful notes of orange and skunk permeate this powerhouse of a strain from Cypress Craft in Manitoba. Equal parts uplifting and euphoric, the effects are as complex and varied as the delightful citrus aroma you'll be greeted with when you open the tube.
products.strainDescription: Mimosa, also known as "Purple Mimosa," is a hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing Clementine with Purple Punch. In small doses, this strain produces happy, level-headed effects that will leave you feeling uplifted and motivated enough to take on any mundane task. In large doses, Mimosa may make you feel sleepy and relaxed. This strain has a strong aroma and flavor that reminds you of its namesake, with notes of fruit and citrus flavors bursting through. Medical marijuana patients choose this strain to help relieve symptoms associated with depression and stress. Mimosa is a staple from the Tangie family. Breeder Symbiotic Genetics has released a refined Mimosa dubbed Mimosa v6.

products.name: RAW WOOD POKERS 113MM
products.description: RAW Wood Pokers help you fill and pack RAW cones with super ease move. RAW Wood Poker is all-natural wooden device.

products.name: KING PALM CORN HUSK FILTER - BERRY TERP
products.description: Berry Terps Filter Tips from King Palm are a safe and easy way to add some refreshing mint flavor to your favorite rolling papers, blunt wraps, and cigarillos. Made from natural corn husk, each filter tip has a built-in flavor pearl made with terpene-infused food grade essential oils that provide a subtle flavor that complements your dry herb. Squeeze and pop the filter to activate the flavor; tips will taste unflavored until the pearl bursts. Each pack of tips includes two individual 7mm filters that can be used to roll up a joint or blunt.
